Class ExecutionPlanValidateCommandArgs

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.utils.ExecutionPlanValidateArgs
      • dfischer.utils.ExecutionPlanValidateCommandArgs

  • public class ExecutionPlanValidateCommandArgs
extends ExecutionPlanValidateArgs
    Validate the argument values (only) of the execution plan commands. Note that the command names and the valid number of arguments have already been checked before calling this class.
    Since:
    V5.5-D
    See Also:
    ExecutionPlanDeclareInstructionList, ExecutionPlanInterpreter
